node.statement: Tube algebra structure constants from general formula (eq 2.8): For Fib, the tube algebra in H_tau is generated by {id_tau, T_tau, L_tau^{tau tau}}. The general composition formula (eq 2.8) gives L_{i<-s}^{jk} x L_{s'<-i'}^{j'k'} = delta_{ss'} sum_{m,n} sqrt(d(j)d(j')/d(m)) F^{jk*s}_{j'k'*n*} F^{i*j*k}_{j'*nm*} F^{i'j'k'*}_{jn*m} L_{i<-i'}^{mn}. Specializing to i=s=i'=tau and using the Fib F-matrix from node 1.1.3, one derives eqs 2.10-2.12.
